author: Ree
title: Blossom Jubilee Giveaway! by Ree
text:
The Pioneer Woman spring line is popping up in Walmart stores all over this great land of ours, and I think you are going to go crazy for the new dinnerware patterns! Everything is springy and gorgeous, full of color and bursting with life. Not a plain white plate to be found anywhere!
Today, in continuing celebration of my new spring collection, I’m giving away five (5) 12-piece sets of “ Blossom Jubilee ,” one of the new spring patterns. I absolutely love it. The yellow dotted border is so bright and happy. 
To enter, complete and submit the giveaway box below!
Five winners will be selected at random and announced Wednesday night!
 
a Rafflecopter giveaway 
Good luck!
Here’s where you can find Blossom Jubilee online!
Blossom Jubilee at Walmart.com
